      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. So if I swap out my list comprehension for a generator, it should stop the script from crashing? I'm also seeing some weird spikes in RAM usage even when I'm not loading the full file. Is it possible there's something else eating up my resources in the background without me seeing it?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
